    <title>Hexo启航:+GitHub Pages部署</title>
    <url>/2021/05/22/Hexo/Hexo_GitPage/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>继本地博客搭建完成，现在让它能够实现远程共享。没有进行调研，直接地就选择了GitHub Page，因为Hexo提供了其一键部署的功能，非常方便简单。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>说其简单，主要是Hexo<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/one-command-deployment.html#:~:text=Hexo%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E6%82%A8%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A1%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%86%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82.%20%24%20hexo%20deploy.%20%E5%9C%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%82%A8%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%88%E5%9C%A8%20_config.yml%20%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89,deployer%EF%BC%8CHexo%20%E4%BC%9A%E4%BE%9D%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%20deployer%E3%80%82.%20deploy%3A%20-%20type%3A%20git.%20repo%3A">部署</a>步骤很少：</p>
<h2 id="github仓库创建及插件安装"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#github仓库创建及插件安装"></a> GitHub仓库创建及插件安装</h2>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>仓库创建就不多说了，自行百度/谷歌吧，不过因为部署博客，仓库创建有点小细节需要注意:<br />
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>    - 所部署的仓库必须是Public,否则网页将不能访问<br />
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>    - 仓库名称(repository name)需要是：<a href="http://xn--eqr924avxo.github.io">用户名.github.io</a> <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\\</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mspace newline"></span></span></span> <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>#用户名即github账户名称，比如：<a href="http://visioner3d.github.io">visioner3d.github.io</a><br />
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>    - 仓库branches设置需要与_config.yml配置一致<br />
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>部署插件安装就一句话，进入博客顶目录，执行:npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</p>
<h2 id="部署"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#部署"></a> 部署</h2>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mspace width="2em"/></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\qquad</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:2em;"></span></span></span></span>部署首先需要进行配置更改，在博客_config.yml文件中，找到deploy关键字，按如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: &lt;repository url&gt; #https://github.com/visioner3d/visioner3d.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: [main]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后执行:hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy就可以了，如果打开网页没有显示，可能需要稍等片刻，毕竟github在国内访问速度确实不敢恭维。</p>
]]></content>
